name: Gatotkaca (Wayang)
shortLoreBlurb: Gatotkaca (Wayang) is a hero from Java/Indonesia linked to flying warrior, thunder. Legends tie them to thunder, winds, and royal mandate.
overlapsLinks: Athena (Greek), Indra (Vedic), Karttikeya (Hindu), Perun (Slavic), Sekhmet (Egyptian), Thor (Norse), Zeus (Greek)
